01:15:03,222 --> 01:15:05,416
make use of my wealth

563
01:15:06,141 --> 01:15:08,371
As I wanted you to do.

564
01:15:09,701 --> 01:15:12,420
Ask me anything now

565
01:15:13,421 --> 01:15:18,494
Worthy of us both.

566
01:15:25,099 --> 01:15:29,809
Love me, when i'm dead

