In my house there's no one

574
01:19:42,192 --> 01:19:44,660
Promise me that you'll send some

575
01:19:45,032 --> 01:19:47,340
But I don't know what i'm gonna do.

576
01:19:53,551 --> 01:19:56,860
Send two towels,

577
01:19:57,590 --> 01:20:00,423
