01:29:45,648 --> 01:29:48,241
Although I don't ask for money right now,

600
01:29:49,047 --> 01:29:51,686
I ask you a favor.

601
01:29:54,727 --> 01:29:57,365
please, write to my husband

602
01:30:00,766 --> 01:30:03,758
